drm/vram-helper: Use drm_gem_ttm_dumb_map_offset()

VRAM helpers now use drm_gem_ttm_dumb_map_offset() to implement
struct drm_driver.dumb_map_offset.

v2:
	* update hibmc as well (kernel test robot)

